descript.abstract: Ag_Commodity is a polygon shapefile representing field border boundaries of agricultural commodity production sites.This dataset was created by the Pesticide Regulatory Program, San Diego County Department of Agriculture/ Weights and Measures. It was created to locate those areas where pesticides may be applied to agricultural commodities in San Diego County, California.
descript.purpose: It was created to assist in quiries as to geographical location where pesticides may be used on crops.
